commit.message: Escaping  ~ in version.sh was necessary after all
Removed spurious backslash esc in version.sh
Use clang in AppRun --configure for LSP

Added version to .gitignore

Deferred from previous commit to make sure that version gets removed

Use release_version as well as version

release_version only gets updated for stable releases, so it can be
included in the repo without causing a paradox
No need to duplicate VTE's env setup
Set up child env in the same way vte does
Prevented roxterm-config trying to parse the same options as roxterm
